    <section id="about">
        <h2>About SILC EXPO</h2>
        <p>The SILC EXPO 2024 is a platform for students from grades 6 to 8 to showcase their talents in various science-related competitions. It aims to inspire young minds and promote scientific curiosity.</p>
    </section>
    
    <section id="competitions">
        <h2>Competitions</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>STEM Challenge:</strong> Each school prepares 5 models. Coordinators select the best 2 models for the expo.</li>
            <li><strong>Best Out of Waste:</strong> On-the-spot competition. 3 students per school create models using waste materials.</li>
            <li><strong>Chemistry Magic Show:</strong> 5 students per school participate in exciting chemistry demonstrations.</li>
            <li><strong>Science Elocution:</strong> 1 student per school presents a speech on given topics.</li>
            <li><strong>Science Art:</strong> 2 students per school draw beautiful art based on provided topics.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    
    <section id="registration">
